responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "6CD222224A042376EDD03A87DB6D2EC3", "I wish I could say I have fond memories of the abbey, and the name Mindel. It feels foreign to me, like the dagger in my side. But I am at ease knowing there were people who cared for me. This embroidery signifies my devotion as a scribe. I must have spent countless years locked away with the scriptures, transcribing the passages.")
name: MADD_0008_BrotherMindel_26
